Title:
  The Curse of Mortifer
  
Description:
  A fallen warrior of centuries ago you are ressurected by the new found necromancer wrecking havoc across Exhaltria. While Mortifer is testing a new ressurection 
  ritual he pulls you back to life but seemingly has no control over you as he has over his many other undead. Your soul is trapped in the Celestial Gate and
  you must now return to the Celestial Gate to go back to the afterlife. Now you must fight Mortifer and his undead legion to get to the gate or fight for him as his puppet. 
  
